==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Filly
<hw>Fil"ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Fillies</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[Cf. Icel. <ets>fylia</ets>,
<ets>fr</ets>. <ets>foli</ets> foal. See <er>Foal</er>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A female foal or colt; a young mare.
Cf. <er>Colt</er>, <er>Foal</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Neighing in likeness of a <qex>filly</qex> foal.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A lively, spirited young girl.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark> <rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Film</ent>⟦br⟧
